            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="0dfb-289c-ce0b-ead7">^^**[Command ability]**^^ Roll 1d10, if the result of the roll is 6+ then this vehicle regains 1d3 lost wound. If the result of the roll was a 1 then the vehicle loses one wound instead.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
